
// Replaces occurrences of a specified type within the [result] node with a value retrieved from the [type] argument. The [strings.replace] slot targets the [result] node, substituting the placeholder [[type]] with the value obtained through [get-value] from the [type] argument within [.arguments].
strings.replace:x:@.result
   .:[[type]]
   get-value:x:@.arguments/*/type
